{
  "stem": "19195.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I want to stay here.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That's OK.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Well, on the way to the grocery store, I made a U-turn.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I-- [? when ?] I heard a rally there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the rally was in German.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I didn't understand German at that time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So there were so many people, and he was screaming and banging there on the table in Germany.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And one lady says in Hungarian, well, it looks like this man came for all the Jews, to take all the Jews away.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I just walked away.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I didn't want to say nothing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "What if they arrest me or something?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I just walked away.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I ended up going to the train.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I had enough money on me to go-- to go home.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And my-- this friend of mine hollered after me, you're crazy.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Why don't you come-- stay here?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "What if something happens?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And I said, if something is gonna happen, I want to be there, too.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Otherwise, I would never forgive myself.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And I ended up going home.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "We were home for two weeks.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then one night, on a Thursday night-- it was after Passover.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "'43.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 11 SECONDS] my mother and I decided to prepare the-- the baking for tomorrow morning and then the cooking.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And all of a sudden, it was like 12:00, 1:00-- 1:00 in the morning, there was a knock on-- on-- on our door.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We never had the doors locked.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It wasn't needed to lock doors there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I asked my mother, should I open the door?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She says, yes.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You can open the door.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And a neighbor came in.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he says he just came from a meeting that they're going to uproot us, and we-- we are going to Poland.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Was this neighbor Jewish?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Pardon me?",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
